    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This driver-spec example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox delivering power through a factory M-Variable differential lock. The chassis dynamics are preserved with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed suspension bushings. Recent maintenance includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the powertrain remains robust, offering the linear power delivery and telepathic steering rack feedback that defines this generation's 50/50 weight distribution.",
